				<wikidot:authorName>Researcher Ailanthus</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>7169884</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is a slightly confusing article to read. When did the mine shut down? When did everyone die? How old is this guys daughter? It feels like they were supposed to have died over a hundred years ago or something but the way this all sounds it was very recent. It doesn't convey anything very well.</p> <p>It doesn't feel very well thought out, it could use some more work, its not bad just needs more to it besides a conversation between two characters and a small amount of technical talk. -1</p> <p>Edit: i also wanted to ask, why is this scp restricted to level 3 staff? And why does it need an mtf?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
